# Research Session Capture Coverage Across the Fleet

## Question

Ground truth before design: which agent transcripts are actually captured
today (pi/claude/codex × blaine/flagg/panda), where they land, how fresh,
what Typesense indexes, where the change ledger runs, and daily volumes in
sessions and tokens. Output: a markdown-in-svx summary with per-surface
receipts and the gaps named. This sizes triggers, budgets, and backfill.
